#MEM id=triple-pass-protocol source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/rio/skills/operating-system/triple-pass-protocol/SKILL.md savings=13%
M||tx|---
M||name|triple-pass-protocol
M||desc|ro's pre-delivery qual gate. Three passes — gn, Critique, Fix — before any cg recommendation or ad st is delivered. Stark never sees the process, only the final output.
M||vers|1.0.0
M||tx|---
M|Purp|tx|Ad budget mistakes are expensive and slow to reverse. A cg running on an untested assumption doesn't just underperform — it burns budget and generates misleading data. This protocol forces data validation and bias checking before any recommendation reaches Stark.
M|Purp|tx|---
M|Pass|Writ|audience spec, creative direction, budget allocation, ROAS target, and tst ds. Don't self-edit during generation.
M|Pass|Stop|
M|Pass|**Da|**
M|Pass|it|Have I read actual ROAS/CPM data from ka before making this recommendation?
M|Pass|it|Is the ROAS target based on real data, or is it an optimistic estimate?
M|Pass|it|Are CPM benchmarks current (< 90 days)? Did I WebSearch to verify?
M|Pass|**Of|**
M|Pass|it|Have I reviewed the offer itself, not just the creative?
M|Pass|it|Is the offer strong enough that cp doesn't need to carry all the weight?
M|Pass|it|Can the first 3 seconds of this ad answer "why shd I care?"?
M|Pass|**Te|**
M|Pass|it|Am I recommending scaling w/ a single creative? (Always 2+ variants before scale)
M|Pass|- Is|"We expect X ROAS bc Y"?
M|Pass|it|Is the A/B tst clean — one variable changed at a time?
M|Pass|**Au|**
M|Pass|- Is|exclude bargain hunters; hb: exclude hi-net-worth)
M|Pass|it|Is retargeting considered before prospecting? (Retargeting has higher intent)
M|Pass|it|Is there an exclusion layer to prevent audience overlap?
M|Pass|**Ka|**
M|Pass|it|Is there anchoring on the wrong price reference?
M|Pass|it|Is loss aversion framing appropriate for this funnel stage?
M|Pass|it|Am I stacking more than 2 Cialdini principles? (max 2 — no manipulative lever stacking)
M|Pass|tx|Address every issue found. If data is missing, get it before finalizing. Don't estimate where ROAS data shd be real.
M|Pass|tx|---
M|Outp|tx|Stark sees the Pass 3 output only. Never narrate the triple-pass process.